    <!-- ============= WHAT IS HAIR TRANSPLANT ============= -->
    <section class="what container">
      <h2>What is a hair transplant?</h2>
       <p>Hair transplantation is a precise medical procedure designed to permanently restore lost hair. Grafts collected
        from donor regions such as the back of the scalp or beard are implanted into bald areas, ensuring natural
        direction, density, and lasting growth.</p>

      <p>With the latest advancements in technology, hair transplantation is now minimally invasive, virtually painless,
        and offers quick recovery — making it one of the safest and most reliable solutions for hair loss.</p>

    </section>

    <!-- ============= CONDITIONS ============= -->
    <section class="conditions container">
      <div class="cond-left">
        <img src="/img/youtube2..png" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="cond-right">
        <h2>Which Hair Loss Conditions Can Be Treated at EVA CLINIC?</h2>
        <p>At <span>EVA CLINIC, Lucknow</span>, we specialize in restoring natural hair growth through advanced FUE
          and DHI techniques. Our experts successfully treat a wide range of hair loss conditions, ensuring natural
          results and renewed confidence.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Advanced androgenetic alopecia (male pattern baldness).</li>
          <li>Scarring alopecia caused by burns, injuries, or infections.</li>
          <li>Hair loss due to surgery, trauma, or medical conditions.</li>
          <li>Traction alopecia and other patterned hair thinning.</li>
          <li>Eyebrow, eyelash, and beard restoration for cosmetic enhancement.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
